        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2106374522" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7892290470260254166">I picked this book up from my local library for a dollar. I believe it was a dollar well spent. The creepy factor was right up there. I like how the authors used modern day techniques to achieve horrific situations. This was definitely a thrill ride and I enjoyed my time on it. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


